s/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個寧願玩牛熊都唔做fundamental analysis<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"快感係好吸引嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9647cb6bea66a537c66fbdd6dfef1e30914b5cb","tid":880220,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05da06afd9126c2adcf35bc75e0c30cd88b4bc30","tid":880220,"uid":5766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"係數？乜係"},{"pid":"65b0e0bd9172b2c7ad73a4b42adea9e627cdb805","tid":880220,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"理論野廢嘅 <br />\n我只知本多終勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd8a7c1f1a1e282825858fdb00d931d44dcdf8d","tid":880220,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e3c64d3fa3bc2ca5b411b994e12488c0f059800","tid":880220,"uid":114447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"同連登仔講有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個寧願玩牛熊都唔做fundamental analysis<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"你唔知基本面好個價可以唔上咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價格係由市場氣氛推動的<br />\n研究嚟有乜用<br />\n<br />\n我夠有方法知道幾多秒之後會升或者跌<br />\n但我搵唔到股王only"},{"pid":"837b686b91f649d2630b943b945cdc2ac910ffdb","tid":880220,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05da06afd9126c2adcf35bc75e0c30cd88b4bc30","tid":880220,"uid":5766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"係數？乜係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4c59ed3c08bbf9499aff248d7653256364882c","tid":880220,"uid":112161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b0e0bd9172b2c7ad73a4b42adea9e627cdb805","tid":880220,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:29:29.000Z","msg":"理論野廢嘅 <br />\n我只知本多終勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"本多買份儲蓄保啲紅利都夠平常人返一年工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dea52b285b3c36c92a87d0b6fe1163cc7d5a648","tid":880220,"uid":112161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cd8a7c1f1a1e282825858fdb00d931d44dcdf8d","tid":880220,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e3c64d3fa3bc2ca5b411b994e12488c0f059800","tid":880220,"uid":114447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T15:22:31.000Z","msg":"同連登仔講有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個寧願玩牛熊都唔做fundamental analysis<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T13:37:24.000Z","msg":"你唔知基本面好個價可以唔上咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價格係由市場氣氛推動的<br />\n研究嚟有乜用<br />\n<br />\n我夠有方法知道幾多秒之後會升或者跌<br />\n但我搵唔到股王only"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:00:52.000Z","msg":"反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市場氣氛導致價格偏離價值 先會有價值投資<br />\n但要計價值 所以都要基本面"},{"pid":"8e3a2f8a0d1ab824b9f7b2613c523972ccad2ccb","tid":880220,"uid":56732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓主有少少鑽左入牛角尖<br />\n<br />\n其實CAPM多多少少assume左EMH，而信得EMH既人我相信佢地會走左去買index ETFs而唔會用CAPM去做stock picking；相反唔信EMH既話咁CAPM本身既assumption都已經係invalid；另外巴菲特本人都recommend投資者用index funds唔知樓主又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以個人認為CAPM用作解釋EMH比起predict the future更重要<br />\n因為提起EMH咁可能會有人問點解唔係隻隻股票既回報都一樣<br />\nCAPM嘗試從風險／回報既角度去解釋點解過往不同股票有不同回報，因為有d股票風險（volatility）高d，所以佢既回報都高d（雖然用volatility去代表risk呢一點亦都有人會challenge）<br />\n雖然CAPM係一個over simplified既model但印象中佢已經解釋到市場入面6x%既variance，呢個角度睇又未至於話太差<br />\n之後學術界當然有d更加複雜既models去解釋更加多既variance，但d approach都偏向統計學既原理，唔知樓主又點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而餘下既discrepancy就係alpha，亦都係價值投資者最想搵既野<br />\n<br />\n另外直接apply CAPM條formula去predict the future當然係冇用<br />\n正如樓主所講，根據CAPM背後條formula搵到既alpha同beta只能夠解釋到股票過往既excess return同volatility而不一定反映到將來既excess return同volatility，但又能否排除有其他方法，例如係價值投資既手段，去model到一隻股票將來既alpha同beta呢？In case有，又有冇可能令價值投資者更有系統地預測將來回報呢？<br />\n<br />\n同埋對於stock picking我諗alpha比beta更重要<br />\n要控制volatility隨時揸多d現金或者槓桿已經做到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：9up"}]}